articles.title: Daniel Levy to play hardball with Bayern and hold Harry Kane hostage? - Bavarian Football Works
articles.description: Surprise surprise! One of the most difficult men to negotiate with in world football is going to do all it takes to keep his star player.
articles.content: Bayern Munich has been flirting with the prospect of signing Tottenham Hotspurs Harry Kane for a while now. The superstar striker would undoubtedly be a massive statement signing, and would instantly… [+1981 chars]
